OL,6,F"Board members, having been informed
OL,7,Fby legal advice (in respect of which
OL,8,Fprivilege is not waived), are assured
OL,9,Fthat the DCC's retirement is in line
OL,10,Fwith contractual entitlements, and
OL,11,Fthat there is no disparity between our
OL,12,Fapproach to this retirement and that
OL,13,Ftaken in relation to other officers
OL,14,Fwho have retired from the service,
OL,15,Fregardless of rank.
OL,17,F"The Board respects the
OL,18,Fconfidentiality of personal
OL,19,Finformation in relation to the DCC, as
OL,20,Fit does with all of its employees."
