OL,3,CDeputy Chief Constable Mark Hamilton
OL,4,Cto retire
OL,6,FDCC Hamilton has been away from work
OL,7,Fsince last September when he underwent
OL,8,Fan unplanned medical procedure.
OL,10,FHe was set to take up a secondment
OL,11,Fwith Stormont's Department of Justice
OL,12,Fand the National Police Chiefs'
OL,13,FCouncil, but the move never happened.
OL,15,FIn September last year the Police
OL,16,FFederation representative body for
OL,17,Frank-and-file officers passed a vote
OL,18,Fof no confidence in Mr Hamilton for
OL,19,Fhis handling of a high-profile
OL,20,Fincident on Belfast's Ormeau Road that
OL,21,Fled to two officers being disciplined.
