OL,3,CDeputy Chief Constable Mark Hamilton
OL,4,Cto retire
OL,6,FThat came after a High Court judge
OL,7,Fruled that the disciplinary process
OL,8,Fagainst the two junior officers had
OL,9,Fbeen unlawful.
OL,11,FThe court ruling was one of a series
OL,12,Fof controversies within the PSNI last
OL,13,Fyear that led to the resignation of
OL,14,FChief Constable Simon Byrne.
OL,16,FJon Boutcher went on to replace Mr
OL,17,FByrne as the region's top-ranking
OL,18,Fofficer.
