OL,3,CDeputy Chief Constable Mark Hamilton
OL,4,Cto retire
OL,6,FThe Chair of the Police Federation for
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland, Liam Kelly, said:
OL,8,F"We note this announcement by the
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland Policing Board.
OL,11,F"Clearly, we had our differences over
OL,12,Fthe handling of the Ormeau Rd
OL,13,Fcontroversy, but I think it important
OL,14,Fto recognise Mr Hamilton's thirty
OL,15,Fyears of policing service and his
OL,16,Fsignificant contribution to our
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,19,F"On behalf of the PFNI I wish him and
OL,20,Fhis family well for the future."
